<section class="manifesto" aria-labelledby="manifesto-text">
  <p id="manifestoText">
    Every small business has one. The task nobody was hired for, that somehow eats everyone's week.
    <span class="pop">We automate it with AI.</span>
    Your team gets their time back. You get your margins back.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    padding: clamp(90px, 10vw, 140px) clamp(24px, 5vw, 72px);
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4.4vw, 62px);
    line-height: 1.14;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  :global(#manifestoText .pop) {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 1.12em;
  }
</style>
